<SingleLayout title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>This website is built with Astro using a theme inspired by hugo-paged.</p>

  <h2>The Theme</h2>
  <p>The hugo-paged theme is designed to create beautiful, print-ready documents while maintaining excellent web accessibility. It uses CSS that mimics the appearance of printed pages.</p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Clean, minimal design focused on readability</li>
    <li>Support for blog posts with categories and tags</li>
    <li>Responsive layout that works on all devices</li>
    <li>Typography optimized for long-form reading</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Technologies</h2>
  <p>This Astro version uses:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Astro for static site generation</li>
    <li>TypeScript for type safety</li>
    <li>Content Collections for managing posts</li>
    <li>Pure CSS for styling (no frameworks needed)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Credits</h2>
  <p>Original Hugo theme created by <a href="https://yihui.org">Yihui Xie</a>.</p>
  <p>Astro adaptation maintains the same aesthetic and functionality.</p>

</SingleLayout>
